text: Josy Staudt (13 October 1904 - 19 June 1937) was a Luxembourgian gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1904 births Category:1937 deaths Category:Luxembourgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Luxembourg City
